text:
pacman::p_load(rstatix, gt, patchwork, tidyverse)


exam_data <- read.csv("Hands-on_Ex04/data/Exam_data.csv")


The plotThe code chunk










ggplot(exam_data,
       aes(sample=ENGLISH)) +
  stat_qq() +
  stat_qq_line()










Note



Note: some note here



The plotThe code chunk










qq <- ggplot(exam_data,
       aes(sample=ENGLISH)) +
  stat_qq() +
  stat_qq_line()

sw_t <- exam_data %>%
  shapiro_test(ENGLISH) %>%
  gt()

tmp <- tempfile(fileext = '.png')
gtsave(sw_t,tmp)
table_png <- png::readPNG(tmp,native = TRUE)

qq + table_png
